{"tid":1566204,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急討論］913系死線 914一定要有行動","createTime":"2019-09-13T12:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T03:26:55.000Z","uid":313681,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"55bf1a3887de6c5268d0ec4734e0173504c74393","tid":1566204,"uid":313681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:57:47.000Z","msg":"唔知你地仲記唔記得，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913系死線</span></strong>？<br />\n<br />\n咁9月14日有咩行動？<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">完 全 冇 人 討 論</span></strong></span><br />\n今日玩人鏈，唱歌，觀星筆已經休息夠喇<br />\n黎討論下聽日到底要做乜喇<br />\n<br />\n以下只系建議<br />\n1：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">和勇合作 打倒黨鐵</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n之前和理非去各個黨鐵商場靜坐<br />\n依家<strong>要升級</strong><br />\n要令黨鐵商場店鋪<span style=\"color: red;\">零收入</span><br />\n例如去食肆坐足成日，唔買野<br />\n或者去服裝鋪睇一件衫一個鐘等等<br />\n而勇武可以去<strong>附近黨鐵站拆鐵</strong><br />\n<br />\n2.去旺角，太子，尖沙咀行街<br />\n聽日天水圍已經被反對，地勢都<strong>極危險</strong><br />\n而旺角，太子,尖沙咀<strong>大家都識路</strong><br />\n又多旅客，為香港帶來經濟收益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我要攬炒！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我要831真相</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警還眼！</span><br />\n旺角，太子，尖沙咀遲早都要再去光復<br />\n不如就聽日啦，反正聽日仲未有活動"},{"pid":"5c7ab8e226ad73b433ecbe4851d3d3db4bae3f7b","tid":1566204,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:58:24.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab0f0bc457548bedf6f47fe720c63bc24047d0d2","tid":1566204,"uid":43939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:59:00.000Z","msg":"而家係長期戰 唔需要死線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sos